# CPAlertAction.Style.cancel

**Case**

The display style indicating that the action leaves data unchanged.

## Declaration

```swift
case cancel
```

## Discussion

Use this style when providing a cancel action on the alert.

## Styles

- **CPAlertAction.Style.default**: The default display style for an action button.
- **CPAlertAction.Style.destructive**: The style indicating that the action changes or deletes data.
